title: The Je Ne Sais Quoi and friends - Live 2005.06.18
description: Swedish post-punks The Je Ne Sais Quoi played an extra-special show at Debaser in Stockholm on June 18 with all sorts of special guests appearing on every song, including scene luminaries such as Ed Greene, Andreas S&ouml;derstr&ouml;m, Knife and Ape, John (Bad Monkey), ASSID, Kate Riff (Soviac) and their sixth member Gabriel. This is a live recording of that show with improved sound from the mixingdesk.
